the atomic energy of an isolated H atom was set as 0.
if perform a normal MD/MS simulation, just comment out the line of below in the input.nn file:
atom_energy                     H  0.040522765326467535  #-0.0408842106         # Free atom reference energy (S)
--->
#atom_energy                     H  0.040522765326467535  #-0.0408842106         # Free atom reference energy (S)
